      "title": "Face Pull",
      "notes": "Target: 3 Technical Failure (RPE 10).\n\nLengthened partials: Immediately after third set, log as drop set.\n\nSetup: Cable #11 | Bench #7. If can, use chest support.\n\nElbow Lead: Hands are hooks; pull through the elbows.\n\nTear: Pull toward hairline; tear the rope apart\".\n\nDouble Bicep: Finish with hands higher than elbows.\n\nVector: 45° upward angle (toward forehead).",
