      "title": "Iso-Lateral Row (Machine)",
      "notes": "Target: 3 Technical Failure (RPE 10).\n\nSetup: Neutral/vertical grip. Palms facing.\n\nPockets: Pull shoulder blades toward back pockets before arm movement.\n\nSternum: Chest \"glued\" to pad.\n\nCrush: Imagine crushing grape between shoulder blades at peak.\n\nHook: Hands are thumbless hooks. Focus elbow drive.\n\nMid-Range: Stop 2–3cm before full contraction. Avoid bicep takeover.",
