    {
      "index": 4,
      "title": "Rear Delt Reverse Fly (Machine)",
      "notes": "Target: 2 Technical Failure (RPE 10).\n\nLengthened partials: Immediately after third set, log as drop set.\n\nSetup: Sit tall; barely touch chest pad. Force core active.\n\nPinky Lead: Light grip; push out with pinky fingers. Bypass traps.\n\nWide: Reach for side walls with knuckles. Reach \"out and wide\", not \"back\".\n\nElbow Lock: Soft bend; lock angle. Prevent tricep takeover.\n\nStop Early: Stop when arms line with shoulders. Avoid shoulder \"roll\" forward.",
