    {
      "index": 5,
      "title": "Preacher Curl (Barbell)",
      "notes": "Target: 2 Technical Failure (RPE 10).\n\nLengthened partials: Immediately after third set, log as drop set, bottom half of movement.\n\nArmpit: Jam armpits deep into pad. No \"air\" between triceps and bench.\n\nWrist: Keep straight or curled inward. Avoid wrists \"flopping\" back.\n\nPinky: \"Turn\" pinkies toward shoulders during curl. Maximize supination.\n\nSafety Stop: Stop short of 180° extension. Protect bicep tendon.\n\nShoulder: Keep shoulders depressed. Do not shrug toward ears.",
