      "title": "Cable Core Palloff Press",
      "notes": "Target: 3 Technical Failure (RPE 10).\n\nHolds: Seated; 15 seconds per rep.\n\nSetup: Sit sideways. Pull handle to chest center.\n\nAnti-Slouch: \"Punch\" shoulder blades forward (protraction). Activate serratus.\n\nAnchor: Brace feet against machine frame. Anchor legs for anti-rotation.\n\nFriction: ~15kg load causes seat sliding. Stabilize with leg pressure.",
